Package io.atlasmap.spi

Interface AtlasModuleInfoRegistry

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultAtlasModuleInfoRegistry
    public interface AtlasModuleInfoRegistry
    The runtime registry of AtlasModuleInfo. AtlasContext builds this registry to store module metadata which corresponds to the DataSource/Document defined in the mapping definition.
